@startuml
title MCP Full Validation Flow

start
:Start Postgres Testcontainer;
:Boot Spring with target profiles;
:Seed ICP and company data;
:Call /api/leads/search or /api/leads/discover;
:Persist mcp_query_observations;
:Assert business response is COMPLETED;
:Query QueryMetricsService / QueryHistoryService;
:Assert metrics and history are populated;
:Call MCP tools/resources;
:Assert payloads match persisted state;
:Check /actuator/health/mcp;
:Check auth 401 and throttling 429 cases;
stop

